# Skill symlinks into the tool submodules — generated by link-skills.sh, never
# tracked (a tracked symlink dangles when its tool isn't initialized; call/0005).
/.claude/skills/

# The Where room: the software as a bare store with worktrees, materialized from
# .host-software by `host-lifecycle software --materialize`. Local and untracked;
# the recorded pin is the audit anchor (STRUCTURE.md).
/software/

# Generated by `host-lifecycle book` (the canonical publisher); never tracked.
# book.toml stays at the repo root; the source and built HTML live under mdBook/
# (mdBook/src + mdBook/out), so docs/ is free for a project's authored content.
/book.toml
/mdBook/
